Introducing the Clifton One9 🌶️ 

Tracing its lineage directly to the OG Clifton 1, the Clifton One9 takes an old-school upper styling with an open-hole mesh underlay and gives it a fresh spin. With the Clifton 9's supreme comfort and iconic tooling, retro style doesn't mean sacrificing comfort for everyday wear. 

Shop the all-new Clifton One9 in HOKA Blue / HOKA Citrus and Habanero / Black at the link in bio.
